text: Afrodite Zegers (born 2 December 1991 as Afrodite Kyranakou) is a Greek born Dutch competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 470 class. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female sailors (sport) Category:Dutch people of Greek descent Category:Olympic sailors of the Netherlands Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470
